This is the reason why shes mine~ WERE SO ALIKE!

Personal Relationship Message~
HayabusaFangirl is my one and only and allways will be, Thanks for being with me my kawaii little girl since (DD/MM/YYYY) 08/06/2014 <3

Friendslist as of 10/09/2015~
About Me!
Hi for anyone who is interested in this random tab!
Osu!mania has been the first ever mania type game i have ever played! I play mostly for fun but i can be competitive at times because i wanna stay No. 1 UK for as long as i can! I also Watch Anime (who doesn't on osu!?) My favorite anime character at the moment is Takanashi Rikka! I also Play alot of different types of games such as, Dead or Alive, League of Legends, Gears of War, Halo and sometimes like to try out certain MMORPGs. If any of you wanna know any more about me, Message me on the website or if your lucky enough to catch me on the main game be sure to message me there!

Special Thanks!
Thanks Amascite, Mat, yamiJaykeey and Pipper for supporter gifts really appreciate it! ~
